+## Disabling the endpoint
+
+Set `gateway.http.endpoints.chatCompletions.enabled` to `false`:
+
+```json5
+{
+  gateway: {
+    http: {
+      endpoints: {
+        chatCompletions: { enabled: false }
+      }
+    }
+  }
+}
+```
+
 ## Session behavior

 By default the endpoint is **stateless per request** (a new session key is generated each call).

